  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42643923240938164\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2345\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Rvq8Ow69CYVz9Wy7rPKQtIH75t0mqvGkcRWsE7QVNV1X1VRZLo9PNkqtEMQD0dohc1PxYrA52nI6C6fnicpq0f9h03WCfcMXO1hCEicNXrZEs/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" data-imgfileid=\"505199761\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8f50eaa0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYVz9Wy7rPKQtIH75t0mqvGkcRWsE7QVNV1X1VRZLo9PNkqtEMQD0dohc1PxYrA52nI6C6fnicpq0f9h03WCfcMXO1hCEicNXrZEs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.544px; widows: 1; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; width: 100%;\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：艾伦</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">黑暗启蒙运动在硅谷的标志性人物——</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh1cpf\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">彼得·蒂尔，将于这几天在罗马开展一系列绝密讲座，驳斥教皇观点，反对 AI 监管，这或许标志着&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">AI 竞争的终局较量已经拉开帷幕。各大巨头想要争夺的标的，已经超越了算力规模与爆款应用。他们真正在抢夺的，是对「未来秩序」的最终解释权。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 24px 8px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinshqh0\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">今天，罗马迎来了一场极其隐秘的闭门集会。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0.5em;margin:0px 0px 24px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mmslkaz3eeo\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.30185185185185187\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;box-shadow: rgb(180, 180, 180) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;border-radius: 6px;\" data-width=\"1420\" data-height=\"428\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"170\" data-imgfileid=\"505199754\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=75c546dc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYVVzbHSXibMu3ia8uzO8g17oAK2ibb0JQPsN5QNexzxWOtN4uShNfn49SWibtsiaVK5oZU5WbMJibRcmu9ghRb8DZpzEzDEDVlCSibiaaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsht4r\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">现场没有媒体的闪光灯，所有参会者均被要求交出通讯设备，连确切的举办地点都被封锁在层层保密协议之中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh1cpf\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">站在演讲台上的，是美国科技圈最具争议的创投教父、大数据巨头帕兰提尔（Palantir）创始人彼得·蒂尔（Peter Thiel）。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0.5em;margin:0px 0px 24px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:center;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mmsm8vrv1rdo\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 74%;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;box-shadow: rgb(180, 180, 180) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;border-radius: 6px;flex-basis: auto;height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"2275\" data-height=\"2276\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"505199757\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2d58b694&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYVnyldbZ3AhXlQAHjehicRZYJoB4rUYEzE9YFdicAqNFIo1QIXeeGqXLjcTibBXNckPtxibV9UH2V537V7soaTM3mvB0CdfFiaqEmUE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh1vvf\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这位在 AI 领域拥有庞大资本影响力的商业大鳄，跨越大西洋来到天主教的精神腹地，抛出了一个极具爆炸性的议题：在技术狂飙的当下，究竟是谁在阻碍人类文明的跃升？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh2192\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于习惯了关注大模型参数迭代和算力升级的读者来说，这场带有神学色彩的演讲似乎有些跳脱。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinshakr\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这背后恰恰隐藏着整个科技行业最核心的焦虑——当 AI 的进化速度足以重塑社会结构，我们究竟该为它套上缰绳，还是任由其彻底接管未来？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh64b\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">彼得·</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh1cpf\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">蒂尔</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh64b\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">给出的答案极端且笃定。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinshb6e\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">他将近年来全球社会高涨的 AI 监管呼声视作一种巨大威胁。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh1x9v\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在他的叙事框架里，那些主张为技术建立护栏、频繁警告「AI 生存危机」的群体，被直接贴上了一个极具宗教恐吓意味的标签——「反基督」。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0.5em;margin:0px 0px 24px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mmslm76uvoo\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42962962962962964\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;box-shadow: rgb(180, 180, 180) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;border-radius: 6px;\" data-width=\"1452\" data-height=\"624\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"241\" data-imgfileid=\"505199755\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b14318b3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYXzXcspD26icmGTWfX2VefrYsjNz5ovTBoEDAWgQuvS5okGTicjLEWbjR7VTs2VckPkk8ia0N560KrNtwib2eJZrQfqntsoWUQsQnc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinshqjt\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">他的核心逻辑在于，某些组织正在利用大众对技术失控的恐惧，试图构建一个大一统的全球监管网络。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh1fd6\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种为了追求绝对安全而设立的干预机制，会彻底扼杀科学创新的生命力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh181y\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">那些试图用规则捆绑大模型发展的人，才是在阻挡通往明日世界的大门。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinshkqz\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种将技术突破视为绝对真理的狂热，直白地挑战了罗马教廷的伦理底线。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh6qq\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">现任教皇利奥十四世曾多次对 AI 的潜在风险发出公开警告，强调科技发展必须拥有道德边界，绝不能在效率的诱惑下牺牲人类的主体性与尊严。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh1ywa\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">梵蒂冈的学者们尖锐指出，蒂尔这种试图用代码解决一切社会问题、甚至谋求所谓「技术救赎」的信条，本身就是对自由社会共识的破坏。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh1dst\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这番担忧有着极其现实的参照物：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh1cpf\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">彼得·蒂尔</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh1dst\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">缔造的 Palantir 帝国，正是一个依靠海量数据吞吐来运转的庞然大物。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh24ha\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">它的算法系统早已深度嵌入多处复杂的国际地缘冲突之中，并在庞大的边境追踪网络里扮演着神经中枢的角色。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinshewq\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">当无孔不入的监控代码开始预测甚至决定个体的命运，科技便悄然滑向了令人不安的深渊。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh5dk\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在这场观念碰撞中，一个耐人寻味的细节让整盘棋局显得更加错综复杂。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh1cpf\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">彼得·蒂尔</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh14n3\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在罗马以近乎决绝的姿态抨击天主教会的主张，他本人在美国政坛倾注巨资、一路保驾护航的核心政治盟友——现任副总统 JD·万斯（JD Vance），恰恰是一位极其虔诚的天主教徒。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0.5em;margin:0px 0px 24px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:center;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mmsm912f66l\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.2944444444444445\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 74%;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;box-shadow: rgb(180, 180, 180) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;border-radius: 6px;flex-basis: auto;height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"2550\" data-height=\"3300\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"727\" data-imgfileid=\"505199756\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8c1039af&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FRvq8Ow69CYUHhe1gLPzicqcP6YJJ4os8h6AS6uenWwVpfqqP6GD4iap3SkluWVD4Nug2Fd2hpnKwmhK2onl6VXQgI0T8geibUc9IicMPg8gWWnU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinshbe\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种看似矛盾的错位，精准地折射出当下科技资本与政治力量深度绑定的新常态。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mmslinshqdj\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">科技寡头们早已越过了单纯提供技术产品的阶段，他们正通过资本渗透和价值观输出，全方位地介入社会运行的底层秩序。</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinshiuk\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在绝对的技术野心和权力游戏面前，所有的身份标签都可以转化为随时重组的实用工具。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh1avd\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这场罗马之行释放了一个极其清晰的信号：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">AI</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;竞争的终局较量已经拉开帷幕。</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh1b5h\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">各大巨头想要争夺的标的，已经超越了算力规模与爆款应用。</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mmslinshbxe\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">他们真正在抢夺的，是对「未来秩序」的最终解释权。</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh18dk\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">他们渴望向全人类证明，究竟哪一套价值观值得被信任，又该由谁来主导明日世界的运行规则。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh1asx\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">无论算法的推演多么精密，无论数据的洪流多么庞大，技术本身永远只提供向前的加速度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmslinsh82h\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">真正决定这列时代狂飙快车最终驶向何方的，终究是人类凝视深渊时的那份敬畏与良知。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/fc1e7e9a-9d5d-4217-b9b2-38069eb1197b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ft.com/content/fc1e7e9a-9d5d-4217-b9b2-38069eb1197b</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "彼得·蒂尔在罗马举办秘密集会，激烈反对 AI 监管并将其支持者标签化为“反基督”，揭示了科技巨头与伦理力量在 AI 未来秩序解释权上的深度博弈。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "彼得·蒂尔在罗马举办秘密集会，激烈反对 AI 监管并将其支持者标签化为“反基督”，揭示了科技巨头与伦理力量在 AI 未来秩序解释权上的深度博弈。",
  "summary": "文章报道了 Palantir 创始人、硅谷创投教父彼得·蒂尔在罗马举行的一场高度机密的闭门会议。蒂尔在会上严厉抨击了全球范围内的 AI 监管趋势，认为这种以安全为名的干预机制会彻底扼杀科学创新的生命力，并激进地将监管倡导者称为“反基督”。这一立场与强调技术道德边界、维护人类尊严的梵蒂冈教廷形成鲜明对比。文章进一步分析了蒂尔与其政治盟友 JD·万斯之间复杂的宗教与利益关系，指出当前的 AI 竞争已超越单纯的算力与应用之争，演变为科技寡头对未来社会运行规则、底层秩序及价值观主导权的终极争夺。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "彼得·蒂尔将 AI 监管视为对文明进步的威胁，并将其支持者标签化。",
